{"Sid":0,"Did":118124,"Id":"282271","Title":"礁溪成功新村武聖廟神龕","ImageUrl":"https://dcm.s3.hicloud.net.tw/excel/place/2020-02-24/d8bcb89b-5364-472e-b2a1-718bfe1349c7/collection/53f685c6-1c10-4c22-ba66-2d579a5b3424/108-her-pa-1806-201910252208545db2e16a5063c0.jpg","IndexCode":"Culture_Place","CustomColumns":{"Description":"\n\n礁溪成功新村為來自浙江下大陳島的居民所構成，武聖廟延續自其原鄉廟與，為其宗教信仰中心。武聖廟主寺關聖帝君，兩側則陪祀有關平與周倉。龍邊神龕奉祀三官大帝（天官大帝、地官大帝、水官大帝）與呂祖大仙。虎邊神龕奉祀華陀祖師、財帛聖君與土德星君。廟埕則奉祀馬使爺與赤兔馬。神龕前四點金柱楹聯以廟名「武聖」為題：「武立乾坤永掌天庭總法界」、「聖行宇宙長扶國土眾生靈」，「武宮安有極天高海闊」、「聖澤本無私源遠流長」。神龕神像的配置，乃是完全仿造大陳原鄉武聖廟的原來配置。\n\n","Keyword_Rights_2":"CC BY","Keyword_Des_Rights_2":"CC0","Keyword_Longitude":"121.768084","Keyword_Latitude":"24.8282058","Original_Url":"https://cmsdb.culture.tw/place/60F60049-A09A-45DA-B4C8-5651CECE2068","Original_Identifier":"282271","Keyword_Subject_1":"民俗與宗教","alias":"","Keywords":"大陳 / 成功新村 / 礁溪 / 關聖帝君 / 關聖廟","historicalDates":"","LastUpdateTime":"2020/02/24 15:09:48","timelines":"","place":"礁溪鄉成功新村","address":"宜蘭縣礁溪鄉成功路32之2號","longitude":"121.768084","latitude":"24.8282058","phone":"","Event":"","relationPeople":"","open":"0","free":"否","openTime":"","openTimeDescription":"","capacity":"","traffic":"","subjection":"","tag":"","situation":"","historicalDataBrief":"","historicalData":"","reference":"","writer":"林世傑/ 蔡明志","createOrgName":"宜蘭縣政府文化局","source":"","Keyword_Rights_1":"","AllImages":"https://dcm.s3.hicloud.net.tw/excel/place/2020-02-24/d8bcb89b-5364-472e-b2a1-718bfe1349c7/collectionOpen/85dd682b-e607-4dfa-abd8-be8e99cb55b8/108-her-pa-1806-re-201910252210125db2e16a5063c0.jpg"}}